  "title": "Night Baker Assistant/Baker (Central Production)",
  "description": "<h1><strong>🥐 Passion Is Our Main Ingredient🥐</strong></h1>\n<p><strong>Baker &amp; Cook Singapore </strong>- Singapore’s only true artisan bakery &amp; foodstore is hiring!</p>\n<h3>💰 <strong>** Attractive Sign-on Bonus**</strong>💰</h3>\n<p>✅ Singaporean* | Singapore PR* | PLOC</p>\n<p>✅ 5-days work week [Rostered], 8pm to 530am</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🍕 Location: Commonwealth Capital Building (7 Buroh Lane, Singapore 618291)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Daily production of bakery bread products in accordance with specifications from recipes</li>\n  <li>Maintain highest quality and consistent products standards</li>\n  <li>Ensure safe and proper use of equipment at all times</li>\n  <li>Maintain a high standard of cleanliness in and around workstation and strictly abide with health/sanitation regulations</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties base on operational needs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Certificate in Baking Skills or its equivalent</li>\n  <li>Preferably 1 year of baking experience</li>\n  <li>Those with no experience but have got passion for baking are welcome to apply</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently as well as in a team</li>\n  <li>5 working days per week with the ability to work on weekends/public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Medical + dental benefits</li>\n  <li>Birthday vouchers</li>\n  <li>Staff discounts across brands</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested party may apply via https://forms.gle/G1q4e4nDrfW1yDmL7 </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>** T&amp;C applies</p>",
